### PHASE 2: FSBS Sidecar Core — Python Implementation
##  Run the Tests Locally
# Open a NEW terminal
cd C:\fsbs-demo\fsbs-platform\sidecar

# Create a virtual environment
python -m venv venv
.\venv\Scripts\activate

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run all tests with verbose output
python -m pytest tests/test_components.py -v

# Run with performance output visible
python -m pytest tests/test_components.py -v -s

# The output should be 39 passed in ~3.5s with PASSED Test names

